```java
case class SodaMachine(cans: Int, coins: Int = 0)
def insertCoin(sm: SodaMachine): (SodaMachine, SodaCan) =
 if (sm.cans > 0) (SodaMachine(sm.cans - 1, sm.coins + 1), new SodaCan)
 else throw new RuntimeException("Out of soda cans!")
```

